<h1 align="center"><font face="Georgia">Step-by-Step New York Style Pizza</font></h1>
<hr noshade color="#000000" width="85%" size="1">
<p align="center"><font face="Verdana" size="2">Click <a href="newyorkstyle.php">here</a> for the recipe</font></p>
<div align="center">
  <center>
  <table border="1" cellpadding="20" cellspacing="0" width="80%" background="images/backgrounds/table.gif" bordercolor="#C0C0C0" style="border-collapse: collapse">
    <tr>
      <td width="50%">
      <p align="center">
      <img src="/images/kitchenaid_mixer.gif" border="1"></td>
      <td width="50%">
      <p align="left"><font face="Verdana" size="2">Mix flour, water, yeast and 
      salt in a mixer. Knead for 15 minutes. The dough should feel smooth and 
      elastic, not sticky. Place in a large bowl, referigerate, and allow to rise 
      for 24 hours.</font></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td width="50%">
      <p align="right"><font face="Verdana" size="2">After rising, turn the dough out onto a floured work surface.</font></td>
      <td width="50%">
      <p align="center">
      <img src="/images/dough_after_rising.gif" border="1"></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td width="50%">
      <p align="center">
      <img src="/images/dough_flattened.gif" border="1"></td>
      <td width="50%">
      <p align="left"><font face="Verdana" size="2">Press the dough into a thick, flat disc.</font></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td width="50%">
      <p align="right"><font face="Verdana" size="2">Place the dough on your fists and stretch the dough into a large, thin circle.</font></td>
      <td width="50%">
      <p align="center"><img src="/images/stretch_dough.jpg" border="1"></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td width="50%">
      <p align="center">
      <img src="/images/dough_on_peel.gif" border="1"></td>
      <td width="50%">
      <p align="left"><font face="Verdana" size="2">Place the dough on a dusted pizza peel.</font></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td width="50%">
      <p align="right"><font face="Verdana" size="2">Add sauce, toppings, and 
      cheese.</font></td>
      <td width="50%">
      <p align="center">
      <img src="/images/dough_with_toppings.gif" border="1"></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td width="50%">
      <p align="center">
      <img src="/images/pizza_in_oven.gif" border="1"></td>
      <td width="50%">
      <p align="left"><font face="Verdana" size="2">Slide pizza onto pizza stone and cook.</font></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td width="50%">
      <p align="right"><font face="Verdana" size="2">Perfect Pizza!</font></td>
      <td width="50%">
      <p align="center">
      <img src="/images/ny_cooked.gif" border="1"></td>
    </tr>
